reviews.text: Loved the food and coffee here. The lunch set menu provided a good variety of choices. The environment is very classy and quiet, good for people looking to spend a tranquil afternoon with their partner or family, sipping coffee and getting work done. The shredded pork BBQ ciabatta was excellent. Even their pre-meal bread was fresh, hot and right out of the oven it seems. Reminds me a little bit of the restaurant Simply Life except this is a small shop, so a lot of effort has been put into the small details. Highly recommended and can't wait to go again for the other set lunches or for dinner.
Pricey, don't get the steak, everything else was good
Good service and food
Lunch set only $130 Great taste and good service😋😋🍔
Great food great service
